




{"id":16180,"date":"2025-03-10T09:31:37","date_gmt":"2025-03-10T02:31:37","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/?p=16180"},"modified":"2025-03-10T09:31:37","modified_gmt":"2025-03-10T02:31:37","slug":"tai-sao-cac-truong-hoc-nen-dau-tu-vao-hoi-truong-thong-minh","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/tai-sao-cac-truong-hoc-nen-dau-tu-vao-hoi-truong-thong-minh\/","title":{"rendered":"T\u1ea1i sao c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc n\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o H\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00f4ng minh"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_78 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-custom ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\" style=\"cursor:inherit\">N\u1ed9i dung ch\u00ednh<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" aria-label=\"Toggle Table of Content\"><span class=\"ez-toc-js-icon-con\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/tai-sao-cac-truong-hoc-nen-dau-tu-vao-hoi-truong-thong-minh\/#hoi_truong_thong_minh_la_gi\" >H\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00f4ng minh l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/tai-sao-cac-truong-hoc-nen-dau-tu-vao-hoi-truong-thong-minh\/#loi_ich_khi_dau_tu_vao_hoi_truong_thong_minh\" >L\u1ee3i \u00edch khi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o h\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00f4ng minh<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/tai-sao-cac-truong-hoc-nen-dau-tu-vao-hoi-truong-thong-minh\/#inno_viet_nam_%e2%80%93_don_vi_cung_cap_giai_phap_hoi_truong_thong_minh_tron_goi\" >INNO Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u2013 \u0110\u01a1n v\u1ecb cung c\u1ea5p gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p h\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00f4ng minh tr\u1ecdn g\u00f3i<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p data-start=\"146\" data-end=\"470\">Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i s\u1ed1 \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd trong gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c, c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o n\u00e2ng cao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i. M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap n\u00e2ng cao tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp v\u00e0 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 h\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00f4ng minh.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"472\" data-end=\"612\">V\u1eady h\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00f4ng minh l\u00e0 g\u00ec? V\u00e0 t\u1ea1i sao c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc n\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p n\u00e0y? H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng INNO Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u ngay!<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"472\" data-end=\"612\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16181\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Vi-sao-cac-truong-chon-hoi-truong-thong-minh-2.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"612\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Vi-sao-cac-truong-chon-hoi-truong-thong-minh-2.webp 900w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Vi-sao-cac-truong-chon-hoi-truong-thong-minh-2-588x400.webp 588w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Vi-sao-cac-truong-chon-hoi-truong-thong-minh-2-768x522.webp 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Vi-sao-cac-truong-chon-hoi-truong-thong-minh-2-600x408.webp 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"619\" data-end=\"659\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"hoi_truong_thong_minh_la_gi\"><\/span><strong data-start=\"622\" data-end=\"657\">H\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00f4ng minh l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"661\" data-end=\"879\">H\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00f4ng minh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00edch h\u1ee3p c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, gi\u00fap gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean v\u00e0 nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y, h\u1ed9i th\u1ea3o, h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"881\" data-end=\"1326\">H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y bao g\u1ed3m:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li data-start=\"881\" data-end=\"1326\">M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh LED c\u1ee1 l\u1edbn \/ M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c \u2013 H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh s\u1eafc n\u00e9t, t\u1ed1i \u01b0u tr\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfu.<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"881\" data-end=\"1326\">H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u00e2m thanh hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i \u2013 \u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o \u00e2m thanh r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb nhi\u1ec5u hay vang.<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"881\" data-end=\"1326\">Thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb\/Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n h\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u2013 Gi\u00fap qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb chi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng, tr\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfu, \u00e2m thanh ch\u1ec9 b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t thao t\u00e1c \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n.<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"881\" data-end=\"1326\">Thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb ghi h\u00ecnh &amp; ph\u00e1t tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn (livestream) \u2013 Ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdc tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>.<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16182\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Vi-sao-cac-truong-chon-hoi-truong-thong-minh-3.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"506\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Vi-sao-cac-truong-chon-hoi-truong-thong-minh-3.webp 900w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Vi-sao-cac-truong-chon-hoi-truong-thong-minh-3-711x400.webp 711w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Vi-sao-cac-truong-chon-hoi-truong-thong-minh-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Vi-sao-cac-truong-chon-hoi-truong-thong-minh-3-600x337.webp 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"1333\" data-end=\"1389\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"loi_ich_khi_dau_tu_vao_hoi_truong_thong_minh\"><\/span><strong data-start=\"1336\" data-end=\"1387\">L\u1ee3i \u00edch khi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o h\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00f4ng minh<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3 data-start=\"1391\" data-end=\"1438\"><strong data-start=\"1398\" data-end=\"1436\">T\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a kh\u00f4ng gian \u0111a n\u0103ng<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1439\" data-end=\"1542\">\u00a0M\u1ed9t h\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 h\u1ecdp h\u00e0nh hay t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng cho:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1543\" data-end=\"1770\">\n<li data-start=\"1543\" data-end=\"1613\">Gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y quy m\u00f4 l\u1edbn (L\u1edbp h\u1ecdc h\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1eddng, h\u1ed9i th\u1ea3o chuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1).<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1614\" data-end=\"1654\">H\u1ecdp h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3ng, h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c.<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1655\" data-end=\"1712\">T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ngo\u1ea1i kh\u00f3a, v\u0103n ngh\u1ec7, di\u1ec5n \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ecdc thu\u1eadt.<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1713\" data-end=\"1770\">Livestream c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o, h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"1772\" data-end=\"1902\">V\u1edbi h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 linh ho\u1ea1t, h\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i nhanh ch\u00f3ng gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00e0i ph\u00fat.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1904\" data-end=\"1968\"><strong data-start=\"1911\" data-end=\"1966\">N\u00e2ng cao hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1969\" data-end=\"2299\">Nh\u1edd h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh LED v\u00e0 \u00e2m thanh hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li data-start=\"1969\" data-end=\"2299\">Tr\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfu b\u00e0i gi\u1ea3ng sinh \u0111\u1ed9ng, t\u0103ng s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc sinh.<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1969\" data-end=\"2299\">K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp &amp; tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn, m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c.<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1969\" data-end=\"2299\">T\u1ea1o ra c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i h\u1ed9i th\u1ea3o chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u, gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc sinh v\u00e0 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c m\u1edbi.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16183\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Vi-sao-cac-truong-chon-hoi-truong-thong-minh-4.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Vi-sao-cac-truong-chon-hoi-truong-thong-minh-4.webp 900w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Vi-sao-cac-truong-chon-hoi-truong-thong-minh-4-533x400.webp 533w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Vi-sao-cac-truong-chon-hoi-truong-thong-minh-4-768x576.webp 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Vi-sao-cac-truong-chon-hoi-truong-thong-minh-4-600x450.webp 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"2301\" data-end=\"2358\"><strong data-start=\"2308\" data-end=\"2356\">Ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0 chi ph\u00ed v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2359\" data-end=\"2690\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n trong h\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ea7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb, t\u1eeb l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb, ki\u1ec3m tra \u00e2m thanh, \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng, b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed m\u00e0n chi\u1ebfu\u2026<br data-start=\"2524\" data-end=\"2527\" \/>V\u1edbi h\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00f4ng minh, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng, gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh v\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u00e1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li data-start=\"2692\" data-end=\"2794\">Ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m chi ph\u00ed thu\u00ea nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt.<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2692\" data-end=\"2794\">Gi\u1ea3m th\u1eddi gian setup, t\u0103ng hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-start=\"2796\" data-end=\"2867\"><strong data-start=\"2803\" data-end=\"2865\">\u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean &amp; h\u1ecdc sinh<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2868\" data-end=\"3004\">H\u1ecdc sinh v\u00e0 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean lu\u00f4n c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp, h\u1ed9i h\u1ecdp chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh s\u1eafc n\u00e9t, \u00e2m thanh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"3006\" data-end=\"3158\">M\u1ed9t h\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00f4ng minh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng, \u00e2m thanh v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gian, gi\u00fap m\u1ecdi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng di\u1ec5n ra thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"3006\" data-end=\"3158\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16184\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Vi-sao-cac-truong-chon-hoi-truong-thong-minh-1.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Vi-sao-cac-truong-chon-hoi-truong-thong-minh-1.webp 900w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Vi-sao-cac-truong-chon-hoi-truong-thong-minh-1-533x400.webp 533w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Vi-sao-cac-truong-chon-hoi-truong-thong-minh-1-768x576.webp 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Vi-sao-cac-truong-chon-hoi-truong-thong-minh-1-600x450.webp 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"3160\" data-end=\"3215\"><strong data-start=\"3167\" data-end=\"3213\">Th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i s\u1ed1 trong gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"3216\" data-end=\"3538\">H\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00f4ng minh kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian v\u1eadt l\u00fd, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u n\u1ed1i \u0111\u01b0a c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 v\u00e0o gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c.<br data-start=\"3330\" data-end=\"3333\" \/>Vi\u1ec7c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 AI, IoT, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng tr\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfu v\u00e0 ghi h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i gi\u00fap nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng l\u01b0u tr\u1eef, ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0 chia s\u1ebb n\u1ed9i dung gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ecdc sinh m\u1ecdi l\u00fac, m\u1ecdi n\u01a1i.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li data-start=\"3540\" data-end=\"3679\">H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn \u2013 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1ea5t y\u1ebfu trong gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c.<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3540\" data-end=\"3679\">T\u1ea1o ra m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean s\u1ed1.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 data-start=\"3686\" data-end=\"3770\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"inno_viet_nam_%e2%80%93_don_vi_cung_cap_giai_phap_hoi_truong_thong_minh_tron_goi\"><\/span><strong data-start=\"3689\" data-end=\"3768\">INNO Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u2013 \u0110\u01a1n v\u1ecb cung c\u1ea5p gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p h\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00f4ng minh tr\u1ecdn g\u00f3i<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"3772\" data-end=\"3975\">V\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c, INNO Vi\u1ec7t Nam mang \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p h\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00f4ng minh to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n, t\u1eeb thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng gian \u0111\u1ebfn cung c\u1ea5p thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"3977\" data-end=\"4293\">Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p c\u1ee7a INNO bao g\u1ed3m:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li data-start=\"3977\" data-end=\"4293\">T\u01b0 v\u1ea5n &amp; thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf h\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi di\u1ec7n t\u00edch, nhu c\u1ea7u s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a t\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc.<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3977\" data-end=\"4293\">Cung c\u1ea5p thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7: M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh LED, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u00e2m thanh, ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd h\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3977\" data-end=\"4293\">L\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t &amp; h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean v\u00e0 nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"4295\" data-end=\"4438\">T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 trong m\u1ed9t \u2013 Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p t\u1ed1i \u01b0u gi\u00fap tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m chi ph\u00ed, n\u00e2ng cao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p!<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"4295\" data-end=\"4438\">Xem chi ti\u1ebft: <a href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/giai-phap-hoi-truong-thong-minh\/\">Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p H\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00f4ng minh<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i s\u1ed1 \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd trong gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c, c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o n\u00e2ng cao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i. M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap n\u00e2ng cao tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp v\u00e0 t\u1ed5&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"feature